Definition: relating to or being a Christian church believing in personal conversion and the inerrancy of the Bible especially the 4 Gospels
Example: evangelical Christianity; an ultraconservative evangelical message
Synonyms: noun, communication, evangel, cognition, evangelicalism, relating, to, or, being, a, Christian, church, believing, in, personal, conversion, and, the, inerrancy, of, Bible, especially, Gospels, Christianity, an, ultraconservative, message
Category: adj.pert
